survey_response.review_text: Good natured Doctor, takes time and explains everything in detail,  Dr. Ashwini is a good professional *** ************** and gives us best suggestions multiple choices on treatment, I would recommend Dr. Ashwini Narayana Swamy (DentaCode).

I went for my mother's root canal, which suggested knee replacement surgery. The doctor examined well and determined that a root canal was not necessary; instead, we opted for a filling. I believe the doctor recommends what is truly needed. The hospital is clean, and the staff are supportive, smiling, and happy

Excellent and empathetic doctor understood my dad's concerns as an elderly person in his late 70s was very conscientious about the pricing and recommended only the required procedures with all pros and cons explained in detail. Well equipped clinic.

I visited for cavity fillings and tooth implant. Doctor listen to us with good patience and will explain the dental issues we have in detail. If patient do not know English, she will speak in kannada also. Totally a good experience and I recommend this doctor.

Very much recommendable dentist. I have visited this clinic couple of times for my couple of teeth..🙂 Dr. Ashwini is Skilled and Very kind doctor. She explains the issues and possible treatments in crystal clear. I have seen so many dentists in my life but nobody given that confidence and comfort before start the treatment, but she does.

Dr Ashwini was patient, friendly and very informative. While treating me she was gentle and clear with her instructions...thanks to her constant doze of encouragement to ensure the results were 100% and morePost the scalling process, she shared best practices which would be suitable to my present state of my teeth and gums. She also went above and beyond to  demonstrate and explain how I should try to address residuals around the neck of my teeth. Thanks Doc.

Dr Ashwini was very professional and friendly made us feel like family.
She explained the treatment well. You know you are in good hands when you learn things about your bone structure that you had no clue about.
Great attention and service.
Always have a great, smooth experience here and would highly recommend.

I was having pain in a tooth that was treated & crowned 😆a decade back.
Dr. Ashwini immediately identified that the crown was damaged and explained the problem and solution to me. She gave me a new crown... her measurement and fixing were perfect with no high points or other discomforts. 

The clinic is pretty sterile and the doctor takes all possible precautions needed during this current pandemic.

Dr Ashwini has been working on my problematic teeth for over 1.5 months . I got Laser gum contouring and veneers done . 
She explained the procedure well and was quite patient. 
Overall I’m satisfied with the treatment and I highly recommend her .

Dr. Ashwini was very friendly and patient. She explains everything in detail unlike other dentists whom I have met so far. I got my wisdom teeth removed. Dr. Vinod ( I hope , that's his name :-p)
Did all the surgical procedure for me. He was confident and did an excellent job. Since I'm a breastfeeding mom , they saw that the medications prescribed were safe for my baby. Dr. Ashwini was always there on WhatsApp too ,to clear my doubts post the surgery.

Thank you doctors!!
